{"about_the_game":"<strong>Planetbase</strong> is a strategy game where you guide a group of space settlers trying to establish an outpost on a remote planet. <br><br>In the game you play the role of the base architect and manager, telling your colonists where to build the <strong>structures</strong> they will need to survive. You will have to ensure that they have a constant supply of <i>oxygen</i>, <i>food</i> and <i>water</i> to stay alive.<br><br>You will get them to collect energy, extract water, mine metal, grow food, manufacture bots, and build a fully self-sufficient base in a harsh environment, where you are always one step away from total failure.<br><br>Even if the game is not intended to be a simulator, all the mechanics are plausible, and based on what the expected challenges of establishing a colony in an new planet would be.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Features:</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\">    <li><strong>Four different planets</strong> with different conditions and increasing difficulty.</li></ul><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/403190/extras/planets2.png?t=1731856878\" /><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\">    <li>Harness <strong>solar and wind energy</strong> (if available) in order to power the base's structures.<br>    </li><li>Grow hydroponic <strong>Vegetables</strong> and synthesize <strong>Vitromeat</strong> to feed your population.<br>    </li><li>Mine and produce raw resources, process them, manufacture goods, and establish a production chain.<br>    </li><li>Carefully manage the colonist immigration flow to ensure you have the people with the right skills.</li></ul><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/403190/extras/characters.png?t=1731856878\" /><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\">    <li>Survive disasters like <strong>meteors</strong>, <strong>sandstorms</strong> or <strong>solar flares</strong> and defend your base from <strong>intruders</strong>.<br>    </li><li>Mechanize your base by creating your own <strong>bots</strong> that will help with the more arduous tasks.<br>    </li><li>Grow your colony from a few initial pioneers to a vibrant planetbase with <strong>hundreds of colonists</strong>.</li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Planetary Apprentice","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/403190/0638b2ea76cb44fc051080f360b64527f3208d44.jpg"},{"name":"Link to the future","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/403190/4bf51f90e1e8831f525dfa6116bdff96679e15db.jpg"},{"name":"Space Farmer","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/403190/c156b2dd1a0135e8240ad0c7207ee5dd080fe960.jpg"},{"name":"Capitalist","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/403190/c3f59fb81f569192f177d9e7d12c2b19bd6251a7.jpg"},{"name":"Cyber Miner","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/403190/10f019fbaa2afaba91f6c080c25d97b4906584b9.jpg"},{"name":"Robo Colony","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/403190/5da3f13fc94321fd91729baa752962076c6326fa.jpg"},{"name":"High Spirits","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/403190/73f22d61e33ae141db531f33a5d84c039baf96fa.jpg"},{"name":"Stargazer","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/403190/4149fdfcb2932e0feaf442cd93b35d7545c1143b.jpg"},{"name":"Steel Dome","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/403190/2ab4ced1299e020937a3171be9039901f36946a7.jpg"},{"name":"Express Outpost","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/403190/ecdc3976dbb8524455fd22ca541403bcc487e7ca.jpg"}],"total":30},"background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/403190/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1731856878","background_raw":"